title: Sugarcane Harris / FIDDLER ON THE ROCK / 1972
description:
Don Francis Bowman Harris  (1938-1999)




After late 60's gigs with Zappa (HOT RATS) and John Mayall's Bluesbreakers, Harris

teamed with guitarist Harvey Mandel and created some memorable music.



Mandel's guitar sound is LESLIFIED throughout the six tracks, switching deftly

between both rotor speeds for full effect.



This is the 3rd of Harris' 10 albums, all recorded in the 70's



Other Harris bands include PURE FOOD AND DRUG ACT and TUPELO CHAIN SEX, although

I haven't heard either
